Asia-Pacific: The "Deepfake Finance" Crisis
Scenario: A CEO of a Singaporean bank is "cloned" using a Deepfake video during a live Zoom call, authorizing a $50M transfer.
The Innovation: You are auditing Cognitive Security (The Hack of the Human Mind).

Title: Cognitive Security: Defending Against Generative AI Fraud in APAC Fintech

Specialist: Melissa Rachel Wozney

The Issue: Technology (MFA) was bypassed because the Human was tricked. This is a "Psychological Breach."

Technical Audit: Evaluating "Liveness Detection" tools and multi-channel verification protocols (APRA CPS 234 compliance).

The Melissa Fix: Developed a "Zero-Trust Communication" protocol that requires a physical "Out-of-Band" token check for any transfer over $1M, regardless of who is on the video call.
